column3: Q1 Identifying Mistakes: To what extent did the AI feedback help you identify the specific mistakes in your answers, compared to just seeing the solution alone?
column4: Q2 Clarity of Explanation for Errors: Did the AI comment clarify why your answers were incorrect better than the standard solution alone could?
column5: Q3 Level of Customization: How well was the AI feedback tailored to your specific answer compared to a general solution?
column6: Q4 Benefit of Customization: How much did the customized AI comment, tailored to your specific answer, help you address your personal learning needs compared to a general solution?
column7: Q5 Actionable Feedback for Improvement: How effective was the AI feedback in providing specific steps or areas to improve, compared to the solution alone?
column8: Q6 Future Problem-Solving: How prepared do you feel to handle similar problems in the future with AI feedback, as opposed to only seeing the solution?
column9: Q7 Depth of Insight into Learning Gaps: To what extent did the AI feedback help you identify specific knowledge gaps, in contrast to the general solution alone?
column10: Q8 Encouragement for Learning: How much more motivated did you feel to address your mistakes after receiving the AI comment, as compared to just the solution?
column11: Q9 Comparative Learning Benefit: To what extent did the AI feedback contribute to an improved learning experience compared to receiving only the solution?
column12: Q10 Preference Between Solution Types: Overall, which did you find more helpful for understanding: the solution alone or the solution with the AI feedback?
column13: Q11 Suggestions for AI Feedback Improvement (Open-Ended): What additional information or aspects in the AI feedback would make it even more helpful compared to the solution alone?

The effectiveness of AI cannot be fully unveiled in this question. However, it is recommended that one may include some analysis of thr question and show clear logical reasoning between steps for other types of questions. One side note regarding Q10 in the survey, if we assume having one more  AI comment does not confuse the reader (which is likely to be true), option 2 will be a subset of option 1.
